def has_fridge_with_open_door(fridge:item):

    symbol has_open_door=open(fridge)
    return has_open_door

def is_fridge_289(fridge:item):
    # Function to determine if the fridge is the specific one with ID 289
    return id[fridge] == 289

def has_cut_chicken_on_board():
    # Function to check if theres cut chicken on the cutting board
    symbol is_cut_chicken=exists food: item : is_food_chicken(food) and cut(food)
    return is_cut_chicken

behavior store_in_fridge(food:item, fridge:item):
    body:
        achieve inside(food, fridge) # Store the chicken pieces inside the fridge

        bind fridge: item where:

        bind chicken: item where:
            is_food_chicken(chicken) and cut(chicken)
